Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses deep learning networks and multi-task learning, which are common topics in machine learning, specifically in the sub-category cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of benchmarks and evaluation criteria, which are common topics in multimedia computing (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the challenges and solutions for pedestrian attribute recognition, which are relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and cybersecurity (cs.CR).
